4. Danas imamo *rodni* dan u školi. (Today we have a *gender* day at school.)
5. On je *rodni* govornik srpskog jezika. (He is a *native* speaker of the Serbian language.)
6. Treba da odredimo *rodnu* ravnopravnost u našoj organizaciji. (We need to establish *gender* equality in our organization.)
7. Kada se porodila, otišla je na *rodiljsko* odsustvo. (When she gave birth, she went on *maternity* leave.)
8. Ona je proučavala *rodnu* ideologiju u svojoj doktorskoj disertaciji. (She studied *gender* ideology in her doctoral dissertation.)

Note: The word "rodni" can have multiple meanings depending on the context, which is why it's used in different forms and positions in these example sentences.